data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. PRICE REDUCED! Similar homes in this subdivision have sold recently for above 440k! Vacant and easy to show! See Lake Eustis from your kitchen window!  Large open floor plan with two master suites!  Located in the very desirable Springwood landing Subdivision, Springwood Landing overlooks beautiful Lake Eustis and has long been known as one of the nicest places to live in Eustis. Most owners in Springwood Landings average owning their homes for about 30 years.  This home at 1226 Palmetto Road is 1905 square feet under heat and air, 2800 feet under roof. It has a large 2 car garage, an inside laundry room and a beautiful large lanai overlooking Lake Eustis, and one of the largest swimming pools in the desirable Springwood Landings development.  (Pool is 33 ½ x 13 ½) The views of the lake are fabulous, and it is as if the sunsets are painted every evening.   The home has four double pane sliding doors offering fabulous views of the lake and the surrounding spectacular landscape, and multiple entry to the pool area for parties. The home received many renovations in 2023 including: updated sprinkler system, new pool liner, new screens on the lanai, new lighting, and ceiling fans on the lanai, fresh paint inside and out, upgraded gutter system, and many landscaping improvements.
